SELECT lm.company,
       COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN cm.customer IS NOT NULL THEN cm.customer END) AS "Customers Who Bought This Month & Last Month",

       CONCAT(DATE_FORMAT(CURDATE() - INTERVAL 1 MONTH, '%Y-%m-01'), ' to ', DATE_FORMAT(CURDATE(), '%Y-%m-01')) AS "Last Month Date Range",

  FROM (
        SELECT DISTINCT customer,

           AND posting_date < DATE_FORMAT(CURDATE(), '%Y-%m-01')
       ) AS lm
  LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT DISTINCT customer,
               company
          FROM `tabSales Invoice`
         WHERE posting_date >= DATE_FORMAT(CURDATE(), '%Y-%m-01')
           AND posting_date < DATE_FORMAT(CURDATE() + INTERVAL 1 MONTH, '%Y-%m-01')
       ) AS cm
    ON lm.customer = cm.customer
 GROUP BY lm.company

SELECT si1.franchise_name AS `Franchise`,
       c.referral_company AS `Referral Company`,
       COUNT(DISTINCT si1.customer) AS `Customer Who Bought This Month & Last Month`,
       (
        SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT si2.customer)
          FROM `tabSales Invoice` si2
          JOIN `tabCustomer` c2
            ON si2.customer = c2.name
         WHERE MONTH(si2.posting_date) = MONTH(CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL 1 MONTH)
           AND COALESCE(c2.referral_company, 'Unknown') = COALESCE(c.referral_company, 'Unknown')
           AND si2.franchise_name = si1.franchise_name
       ) AS `Customer Who Bought Last Month`,
       CONCAT(IFNULL(ROUND((COUNT(DISTINCT si1.customer) / (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT si2.customer) FROM `tabSales Invoice` si2 JOIN `tabCustomer` c2 ON si2.customer = c2.name WHERE MONTH(si2.posting_date) = MONTH(CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL 1 MONTH) AND COALESCE(c2.referral_company, 'Unknown') = COALESCE(c.referral_company, 'Unknown') AND si2.franchise_name = si1.franchise_name )) * 100, 2), 0), '%') AS `Retention Rate (%)`
  FROM `tabSales Invoice` si1
  JOIN `tabCustomer` c
    ON si1.customer = c.name
 WHERE MONTH(si1.posting_date) = MONTH(CURRENT_DATE)
   AND si1.customer IN (
        SELECT DISTINCT customer
          FROM `tabSales Invoice`
         WHERE MONTH(posting_date) = MONTH(CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL 1 MONTH)
       )
 GROUP BY si1.franchise_name,
          c.referral_company

WITH c_all AS (
        SELECT territory,
               COUNT(DISTINCT unique_entity) AS unique_entity_count
          FROM (
                SELECT territory,
                       referral_company AS unique_entity
                  FROM `tabCustomer`
                 WHERE referral_company IS NOT NULL
                 UNION SELECT territory,
                       franchise_name AS unique_entity
                  FROM `tabCustomer`
                 WHERE referral_company IS NULL
               ) combined_data
         GROUP BY territory
       ) SELECT c.territory AS Territory,
       CONCAT(DATE_FORMAT(t.posting_date, '%M'), ' - ', YEAR(t.posting_date)) AS MonthYear,
       COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN c.referral_company IS NOT NULL THEN c.referral_company ELSE c.franchise_name END) AS `Daily Active Franchise`,
       COALESCE(c_all.unique_entity_count, 0) AS `Total Franchises`,
       CONCAT(ROUND(COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN c.referral_company IS NOT NULL THEN c.referral_company ELSE c.franchise_name END) / NULLIF(COALESCE(c_all.unique_entity_count, 0), 0) * 100, 2), ' %') AS `POS Usage %`
  FROM `tabPOS Invoice` t
  LEFT JOIN `tabCustomer` c
    ON t.customer = c.name
  LEFT JOIN c_all
    ON c.territory = c_all.territory
 GROUP BY c.territory,
          MonthYear
 ORDER BY c.territory,
          YEAR(t.posting_date) DESC, MONTH(t.posting_date) DESC

       IFNULL(COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN `tabSales Invoice`.posting_date <= CURDATE() - INTERVAL (WEEKDAY(CURDATE()) + 9) DAY AND `tabSales Invoice`.posting_date >= CURDATE() - INTERVAL (WEEKDAY(CURDATE()) + 22) DAY THEN `tabSales Invoice`.customer END), 0) AS `Customers Who Bought Last Two Week Only`,
       CONCAT(DATE_FORMAT(CURDATE() - INTERVAL (WEEKDAY(CURDATE()) + 8) DAY, '%%d-%%m-%%Y'), ' to ', DATE_FORMAT(CURDATE() + INTERVAL (5 - WEEKDAY(CURDATE())) DAY, '%%d-%%m-%%Y')),
       CONCAT(ROUND(IFNULL(COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (CASE WHEN `tabSales Invoice`.posting_date >= CURDATE() - INTERVAL (WEEKDAY(CURDATE()) + 8) DAY AND `tabSales Invoice`.posting_date <= CURDATE() + INTERVAL (5 - WEEKDAY(CURDATE())) DAY THEN `tabSales Invoice`.customer END) IN (SELECT DISTINCT `tabSales Invoice`.customer FROM `tabSales Invoice` WHERE `tabSales Invoice`.posting_date <= CURDATE() - INTERVAL (WEEKDAY(CURDATE()) + 9) DAY AND `tabSales Invoice`.posting_date >= CURDATE() - INTERVAL (WEEKDAY(CURDATE()) + 22) DAY) THEN `tabSales Invoice`.customer END), 0) / IFNULL(COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN `tabSales Invoice`.posting_date <= CURDATE() - INTERVAL (WEEKDAY(CURDATE()) + 9) DAY AND `tabSales Invoice`.posting_date >= CURDATE() - INTERVAL (WEEKDAY(CURDATE()) + 22) DAY THEN `tabSales Invoice`.customer END), 0) * 100, 2), '%%') AS `Retention Rate`
  FROM `tabSales Invoice` AS `tabSales Invoice`
  LEFT OUTER JOIN `tabCustomer` AS `tabCustomer`
    ON `tabSales Invoice`.customer = `tabCustomer`.name
 GROUP BY CONCAT(DATE_FORMAT(CURDATE() - INTERVAL (WEEKDAY(CURDATE()) + 22) DAY, '%%d-%%m-%%Y'), ' to ', DATE_FORMAT(CURDATE() - INTERVAL (WEEKDAY(CURDATE()) + 9) DAY, '%%d-%%m-%%Y'))
 LIMIT 100000000
